{"tid":966034,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係咁","createTime":"2019-01-02T13:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T13:34:13.000Z","uid":221589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f58b420e26c35ac937be77df785e1b1575f66e08","tid":966034,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"借ac<br />\n<br />\n其實我地關係一直都唔錯 好愛對方 <br />\n但好可惜我地都好忙 呢排成日都冇得見 差唔多一個幾星期冇見 <br />\n之前都因為成日冇得見呢個問題吵到大家都想分手<br />\n<br />\n大家返工返學又攰又忙 <br />\n連除夕都冇出 冇倒數 佢已經訓左先 <br />\n我仲要挨到兩三個禮拜先有得見  <br />\n講真好辛苦 見到人地又錫又攬 我就連拖下手都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係得有時傾下半個鐘電話就完左一日<br />\n<br />\n香港long d真係好難挨....<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b44526ecf0c60a39b6a41327d634a58f9bbc74","tid":966034,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"e4ce9e5e8acd5262d55a03205311f27dc0cbca7d","tid":966034,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"希望有人理下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00efd2e5acdbbd452c00d541df837e6808e098c5","tid":966034,"uid":218415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"Long d預左<br />\n會嘈分手既都行唔到長<br />\n真係愛對方既<br />\n就算再嗌交都唔會講分手"},{"pid":"b9dab7f0fae831accfd8c2328986c6d7345fabbb","tid":966034,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00efd2e5acdbbd452c00d541df837e6808e098c5","tid":966034,"uid":218415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"Long d預左<br />\n會嘈分手既都行唔到長<br />\n真係愛對方既<br />\n就算再嗌交都唔會講分手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"香港喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/x